+   protocol that quietly bakes in the hoped-for coherence or persistence.
+4. Bounding the Step-3 candidate list so the primary hybrid, comparators, and
+   Beltrami fragility screens stay aligned with the local chain record.
+
+Use only the local repository copies and return concrete findings, not just
+file paths.
