  - `library/factual/geometry-route-screening/tube-persistence-remains-live-only-as-a-dynamic-or-hybrid-route.md`
- [VERIFIED] The local record repeatedly says that static concentration,
  anisotropy, or coherent-structure snapshots are not enough; only dynamic
