+Combined protocol:
+
+- [PROPOSED] Audit the intense set
+  `E_r(t) = { x in B_r(x_*) : |omega(x,t)| >= r^{-2} }`
+  on the parabolic cylinder
+  `Q_r(x_*, t_*) = B_r(x_*) x [t_* - r^2, t_*]`,
