+Write:
+
+1. `REPORT.md` with the bounded observable table and ranking.
+2. `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` with:
+   - goal
+   - what was checked
+   - outcome
+   - one key takeaway
+   - a compact candidate ranking
+   - whether the branch should advance to the dynamic plausibility screen
